<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/58039491"><img alt="Ρέκβιεμ για μια Δημοκρατία" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1620986416l/58039491._SX98_.jpg" />
